ABSTRACT

The Content Management System (CMS) for Blog is a web-based application designed to allow users to create, edit, manage, and publish blog content efficiently. The system provides a user-friendly interface for content management, enabling administrators and authors to handle blog posts, categories, comments, and user accounts. The project aims to simplify content publishing while ensuring easy maintenance and scalability.

