7. SYSTEM DESIGN

User Roles

Admin

- Manage users
- Manage blog posts
- Manage categories
- Monitor comments

Author

- Create posts
- Edit posts
- Delete posts

Visitor

- Read blog posts
- View categories
- Submit comments

