8. MODULES DESCRIPTION

User Management Module

Handles registration, login, and user authentication.

Blog Management Module

Allows creation, editing, updating, and deletion of blog posts.

Category Management Module

Organizes blog posts into categories.

Comment Management Module

Handles user comments and feedback.

Dashboard Module

Provides statistical and management information.

